page.name: Helm of Autumn's Call I
page.description: While the leaves of summer change hue into autumn, the foliage on this ancient helm never seems to change. When you wear it, you swear you can feel the cool breeze of fall ever beckoning.

page.name: Turdraken Wyvernling
page.description: This diminutive part-fowl, part-dragon seems to have traveled here from regions unknown in search of food! Luckily it found you to take care of it! Applies a DoT effect and scales with your level.
